title: OK St. HC Mike Gundy joins J&J
description:
Jalen & Jacoby are joined by the coach of the #8 Oklahoma State Cowboys, Mike Gundy. He talks mullets, Big 12 realignment, draft prospects, and the big game against #13 TCU. Plus! A breakdown of this week's NFL slate, and Draymond finally speaks.
